 我細你好多的, 中學荃灣讀, 自己估下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec44b8f361caf00e39be071863b3edd59e4abb87","tid":58571,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主曲線話自己拔尖<br />\n大家小心地滑<br />\n出到社會無人會 care 你咩成績, 只會 care 你咩 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n[mean mode]<br />\n一個AL讀唔成書, 走去做保安既走嚟同我講冇人care你咩成績同咩post<br />\n使唔使貼稅單比你睇呀柒頭<br />\n[/mean mode]</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問樓主當時三十分<br />\n而家有幾成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n月入三十萬?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我就咩都冇imply過既, 我做野冇人工架, 又做緊自己想做既野, 又唔使聽老細講野。只係我見親林智潤都想撚下佢咁, 好認真, 我另一邊個Post都有寫, 廿幾歲人仲要用中學成績打下飛機, 其實好柒囉, 當然都柒唔過連AL都考唔過但係又要講到自己懷才不遇咁, 真係人唔笑狗都吠。"},{"pid":"bbaf1fa6a6c2adbda0959c0c5319408434b73395","tid":58571,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貼稅單"},{"pid":"f79dcdd302aec3c4f49d4f3ebe05576710b8905a","tid":58571,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:36:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47718592eb52a73924b84ea19909966efe838d11","tid":58571,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:38:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b1a12224ab7430c91ab43e69397e9ca1a97c9f2","tid":58571,"uid":25923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:43:33.000Z","msg":"29<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221db88a59fda32cc085cddb03f67a76592df90f","tid":58571,"uid":62675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:45:00.000Z","msg":"以前中學有個啊sir拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerf